1401692 = { #韓德讓 Han Derang or 韓德昌 Han Dechang or 耶律隆運 Yelü Longyun, courtesy name 興寧 Xingning, Khitan name 姚哥 Yaoge. Fourth son of Han Kuangsi (故尚父秦王贈尚書令昌黎韓公墓誌銘 and 惕隱司秦王帳空寧敵烈太保墓誌) or second son. (遼史/卷9) Later entered the court and became 南院樞密使. After the enthronment of Shengzong and regency of Queen dowager, Derang was relaged to palace guards. In 985 政事令. Next year lead forces in victory over Cao Bin and Mi Xin, for which was made Duke of Chu and soon after elevated to Prince of Chu. In 994 北府宰相兼領樞密使 and soon after also 北院樞密使, elevated to rank 大丞相 and made Prince of Qi. At that time held power over whole Liao army. In 1001.4.16 granted name 韓德昌. (遼史/卷14) In 1005.1.13 granted 耶律 surname. (遼史/卷14) In 1010 granted name 耶律隆運. (遼史/卷82) In 1011.4.11 died. (遼史/卷15)
